An HTML "one sheet" resume with mobile friendly css

Features:
- HTML / CSS "one sheet" resume template
- fully tested on Safari / iPad / iPhone
- somewhat tested on FireFox
- low filesize footprint / resulting PDF size
- Funny default text (I think)

Lacking:
- IE / Chrome support
- a "demo" link
- more CSS options for the headshot

Just clone this, fill in your details, send out, get  job, profit!